rows.label: qst202713_msg0001
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh!
Why?! Why, meh?!

rows.label: qst202713_msg0002
rows.name:
Germon only want to change this
good-for-nothing rotten world!

rows.label: qst202713_msg0003
rows.name: So why you... Why you have to...

rows.label: qst202713_msg0004
rows.name:
That there wasn't any sort of demon,
just your garden variety monster.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0005
rows.name:
It saw you on an empty stomach
and decided to get a snack.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0006
rows.name:
I can guarantee it wasn't trying
to save the world or anything.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0007
rows.name: Me-mehhh...

rows.label: qst202713_msg0008
rows.name:
But, hey...
Do you really want to save the world?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0009
rows.name:
Yes!
That why Germon assemble young
Nopon who still hope for better Alst.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0010
rows.name:
Well, you've got charisma,
so there's that at least.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0011
rows.name:
Next time, how 'bout you try changing
the world yourself, instead of asking
demons for help?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0012
rows.name: For my money, that's even cooler.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0013
rows.name: Meh-me-meh...

rows.label: qst202713_msg0014
rows.name:
Sorry to interrupt your love-in, but
did a Nopon called Mimumu come here?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0015
rows.name:
Mimumu?
There no littlepon by that name here.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0016
rows.name: Ugh, so where did she go...?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0017
rows.name:
Maybe she join
other branch of franchise?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0018
rows.name: ...I beg your pardon?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0019
rows.name:
You mean there are other groups
doing what you've been doing?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0020
rows.name:
Precisely.
Germon represent Superbian branch.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0021
rows.name:
Harbingers of Eschapon comprised
three branches, changing world by
summoning three demons.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0022
rows.name:
Sad to say, management have little
confidence in Germon, so this branch
get weakest demon assignment...

rows.label: qst202713_msg0023
rows.name:
To be fair, it's not like you were
actually summoning anything...

rows.label: qst202713_msg0024
rows.name: So where are the other branches?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0025
rows.name:
One is Gula branch, me hear they
meet to perform rite on far end of
Wrecc Marshland.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0026
rows.name:
As for other...
Germon was not told, to reduce
risk of information leak.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0027
rows.name:
I see...
The head of the Gula branch
would know, I suppose.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0028
rows.name:
Then we should depart for Gula,
post-haste.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0029
rows.name: Right on...

rows.label: qst202713_msg0030
rows.name:
We might find Mimumu, and if this lot
is anything to go by, she's bound to
need saving from something peckish.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0031
rows.name: OK, let's head out.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0032
rows.name:
Please wait!
Germon greatly impressed by
friend's coolness.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0033
rows.name:
If it please friend, would friend
consider to stay here and lead
flock of Germon?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0034
rows.name: No way.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0035
rows.name: Why no way?!

rows.label: qst202713_msg0036
rows.name:
First, I hate being put on a pedestal.
Second, I've no interest in changing
Alst.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0037
rows.name: Mmehhh... Then what Germon do...?

rows.label: qst202713_msg0038
rows.name:
I told you, didn't I? You can lead 'em,
you've proven that. Just use it for
good or something.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0039
rows.name:
I'm sure you can change the world
in some way, however small.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0040
rows.name:
...Germon understand.
We try to start afresh.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0041
rows.name:
Germon lead flock to greatness!
No gods or demons, only Nopon!

rows.label: qst202713_msg0042
rows.name:
Sounds great, guys.
Do your model best.

rows.label: qst202713_msg0043
rows.name:
So. Destination, Gula,
far end of Wrecc Marshland!
